OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA windy
OL,6,Fevening with a risk of coastal gales
OL,7,Facross Cornwall for a time. Often
OL,8,Fcloudy with further spells of rain
OL,9,Fmoving into the far west during the
OL,10,Fearly morning. Lighter winds by dawn.
OL,11,FStaying mild.
OL,12,
OL,13,CMonday:FUnsettled to begin the new
OL,14,Fweek as rain slowly edges eastwards,
OL,15,Fheavy at times over the hills. Winds
OL,16,Feasing through the day. Remaining mild
OL,17,Ffor the time of year.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
