OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FFine
OL,6,Ffor Tuesday and Wednesday, with plenty
OL,7,Fof sunny spells. Dry for much of
OL,8,FThursday too, with some rain possible
OL,9,Flater. Feeling pleasant in any sunny
OL,10,Fspells.
